Skulls Galaxy App on Chrome Extension - Stylish Fashion World

Welcome to the Skulls Galaxy Chrome Extension app! This application will help you easily search and buy unique fashion products with quick price calculation and stylish fashion product lists. You can estimate the price based on the quantity you want to buy and explore trending fashion products like Personalized Maleficent shirt, New Orleans Pelicans shirt, Us Navy Uss Green shirt.

Salient features:
Fast and convenient price calculation: With the quick price calculation feature, you can estimate the total cost based on the number of fashion products you want to buy. Just enter the quantity in the corresponding box, the application will automatically calculate the estimated total price, helping you manage your fashion shopping budget effectively.

Display unique fashion products: Skulls Galaxy application on Chrome Extension displays a list of unique and stylish fashion products. You will easily find Personalized Maleficent shirts, New Orleans Pelicans shirts, Us Navy Uss Green shirts, and many other unique fashion products, meeting the preferences of everyone.

Detailed product information: The application provides detailed information about each fashion product, including descriptions of colors, materials, sizes, and information about promotions. This helps you choose fashion products that suit your personal style and preferences.

How to install and use:

Setting:

Open Google Chrome browser.
Visit the Chrome Web Store.
Search for "Skulls Galaxy" in the search box.
Select the "Skulls Galaxy" widget and press the "Install" button.

Use:
Click the icon to open the utility.
In the list of fashion products, you can explore and choose products that suit your preferences.
